{
  "_comment": "Single source of dispatch truth for run_experiment.py. loader routes to AutoModelForCausalLM vs AutoModelForImageTextToText (Qwen3.5 is multimodal). c5_supported / quant_supported gate the add-on passes per architecture; unsupported combos are recorded in experiment_config.json as skipped-with-reason, not attempted 1000x. Hybrid Mamba models (falcon_h1, granitemoehybrid) get pure-PyTorch fallback if the optional kernels did not compile.",
